.",nt=()=>"This fee covers the additional costs of partnering with local, third-party drivers to bring your order right to you.\n\nThis fee does not apply to orders for Walmart+ members.",na=()=>"This fee covers additional fulfillment costs that are required when delivering to certain locations such as Hawaii, Alaska, Puerto Rico and Guam",ni=()=>"Your order will be delivered in bags, which includes a fee of $0.10 per bag. Bag fees may vary based on location.",nr=()=>"This fee helps cover additional costs for fulfilling your larger item orders above standard dimensions or weight.",nl=()=>"Free Express Delivery",no=()=>"Estimated regulatory fees & taxes",nd=()=>"The government requires Walmart to collect fees and other taxes for certain products.",ns=()=>"More information on regulatory fees and taxes",nc=()=>"By law, we're required to collect this fee on the sale of any taxable goods delivered within Colorado. This fee goes directly to the state.",nu=()=>"This fee is authorized by Minnesota law on the delivery of your items. This fee is paid to the State of Minnesota.",nm=()=>"Temporary hold",np=()=>"The temporary hold is the amount we authorize to cover weighed items, potential substitutions and any bag fees in your state.",nx=()=>"You\u2019ll be charged the final order total once your order is picked up or delivered. The total includes the price of items received.",ny=()=>"Your bank should remove the authorization hold on your card within 7 business days.",nf=()=>"The temporary hold is the amount we authorize to ensure there are funds to complete your shopping cart. This isn\u2019t a charge. Your order total may vary to account for weighted items, like meat and produce, and any bag fees in your state.",ng=()=>"You will only be charged for the final order total once your order is picked up or delivered. Your bank should remove the authorization hold on your card within 7 days.",nw=()=>"A temporary hold is the amount your bank authorizes to ensure there are enough funds to complete your shopping cart when using a credit or debit card. This isn\u2019t a charge. The hold amount may differ from your final order total due to items that are priced by weight, canceled, or potentially substituted, and state bag fees where applicable.",nb=e=>s.createElement(s.Fragment,[],"You\u2019ll only be charged the final order total for the items you receive. Your bank",function(e,n){let t=arguments.length>2&&void 0!==arguments[2]?arguments[2]:e=>e;return(e&&"object"==typeof e?e.fmt:t)(n)}(e.boldText,I.Ys((e=>e&&"object"==typeof e&&"val"in e?e.val:e)(e.boldText),{other:" should remove the temporary hold on your card within 10 days "})),"after receiving your order."),nv=e=>s.createElement(s.Fragment,[],"You\u2019ll only be charged the final order total for the items you receive. This includes any cost differences that may exceed the temporary hold amount. Your bank",function(e,n){let t=arguments.length>2&&void 0!==arguments[2]?arguments[2]:e=>e;return(e&&"object"==typeof e?e.fmt:t)(n)}(e.boldText,I.Ys((e=>e&&"object"==typeof e&&"val"in e?e.val:e)(e.boldText),{other:" should remove the temporary hold on your card within 10 days "})),"after receiving your order."),nE=()=>"When your payment method includes a gift card, EBT, WIC, PayPal or another prepaid card, a temporary charge is placed to ensure there are enough funds to complete your shopping cart.",nh=()=>"This charge is intended to cover adjustments to your final order total from items that are priced by weight, or potentially substituted, and state bag fees where applicable.",nL=()=>"After your final order total is confirmed, we'll refund any amount that's left over.",nS=()=>"If needed, your credit or debit card will be used to cover any cost differences that may exceed the adjustment charge amount.",nA=()=>"Okay",nI=()=>"This covers adjustments to your final order total for items that are priced by weight or potentially substituted, and state bag fees where applicable. After your final order t